Privacy Policy
At
Document Reader
, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data.
1. Information Collection
We do not collect any personally identifiable information (PII) from users. The app operates offline and does not require users to provide personal details such as names, email addresses, or contact information.
2. Data Usage
Document Reader
only accesses files stored locally on your device for the purpose of viewing, editing, and managing documents. We do not upload, store, or share your files without your consent.
3. No Ads
Our app is ad-free. You can use
Document Reader
without being interrupted by advertisements or third-party tracking.
4. Permissions
The app may request permission to access your deviceâ€™s storage to enable file viewing and management. We do not access any other data or systems on your device.
5. Third-Party Sharing
We do not share your data with any third parties. All your files and information remain private and secure on your device.
6. Security
We prioritize the security of your documents. While we take all reasonable precautions to protect your data, we recommend using secure devices and environments when managing sensitive files.
7. Changes to Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted within the app, and continued use signifies acceptance of those changes.
8. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at
premiumqualityapps.com@gmail.com
